from pyspark import SparkContext, SparkConf,SQLContext
from pyspark.sql.functions import col, udf
from pyspark.sql.types import DateType
from sklearn.cluster import DBSCAN
import numpy as np 
from datetime import datetime
# Import `pyplot` 
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# Set the style to `ggplot`
plt.style.use("ggplot")

conf = SparkConf().setAppName("App")
conf = (conf.setMaster('local[*]')
        .set('spark.executor.memory', '4G')
        .set('spark.driver.memory', '30G')
        .set('spark.driver.maxResultSize', '10G'))

sc = SparkContext.getOrCreate(conf=conf)
sqlContext = SQLContext(sc)

paragraphs.title: Seleciona todos os clusters que possuem pelo menos 2 nibus

paragraphs.text:
%sql

-- todas as chaves
select key,discrete_dt_event,cod_linha,nome,cluster_id,count(distinct veic)
from bus_bunchings
where data < '2018-11-24'
group by key,discrete_dt_event,cod_linha,nome,cluster_id
having count(distinct veic) > 1
order by cod_linha,discrete_dt_event

paragraphs.text:
%sql

with 
bunchs as (
-- todas as chaves
select key,cod_linha,nome,data,cluster_id,count(distinct veic) 
from bus_bunchings
where data < '2018-11-24'
group by key,cod_linha,nome,data,cluster_id
having count(distinct veic) > 1
order by cod_linha,data
) select nome,count(1) as qtd from bunchs
group by nome
order by qtd desc limit 50
